{"tid":2180953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子被指北角站寫「831」字眼　涉刑毀被捕","createTime":"2020-08-30T08:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:11:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f17d06b3630cebdaa17e3075dbccbf6944c1c2e2","tid":2180953,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"831 太子站襲擊事件即將一年，警方表示今早（30 日）約 8 時，一名 38 歲男子在港鐵北角站範圍內以筆塗鴉並寫上一個日子，涉刑事毁壞被捕。據報男子的塗鴉與 831 太子站事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆《立場》查詢時指，今早 8 時 03 分，港鐵職員在北角站月台發現一名男子形跡可疑，其後發現他在站內範圍一面牆上以筆塗鴉，內容包括一個日期，職員報警，警員到場以涉刑事毁壞將男子拘捕。《明報》引消息指，男子於站內寫上與 831 太子站事件相關字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E5%AF%AB-831-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25AF%25AB-831-%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=38419e1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25AF%25AB-831-%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=7656b6cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E5%AF%AB-831-%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"a28e15860bde13ca72002347169ddfd60b7e4acf","tid":2180953,"uid":216592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi